PROJECT DEFINITION: Formalized Statement of Work established for
BagOfDice module development. Outlines three-module structure:
1) BagOfDice (core dice mechanics), 2) BagOfGems (gem generation),
3) TreasureHoard (treasure system). Defines development methodology
with daily cycle protocol and roadblock tracking. Sets success
metrics for both technical delivery and process evaluation for
AI-assisted development study. Mobile-first development approach
documented as constraint for workflow analysis.
